metadata.name: The Passing Bells
metadata.description:
The decision was made, she couldn't take it anymore.
Feeling free as a bird ,she got as far as possible from the royal area, walking and jumping with happiness for the first time in her life.
Untill at a moment ,She realised she was lost.
As the sun was setting, the runaway princess sat desperately and frightened on a rock of a cold, hazy mountain…she turned into wind, so she could be free forever.
the distant bells sound shows she’s still somewhere around, passing by while floating freely in the sky.
